# 🗂️ Task Management App

A simple, full-stack task management application that allows users to create, read, update, and delete tasks. Built with a Python backend (Flask or FastAPI) and a responsive HTML/CSS/JavaScript frontend.

## 🚀 Features
- Create new tasks with descriptions
- View all existing tasks
- Edit or delete tasks
- Toggle task status (e.g., completed/pending)
- Fully responsive design
- RESTful API integration

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Backend**: Flask / FastAPI (local server)
- **Database**: JSON / In-memory or any preferred DB
- **Version Control**: Git, GitHub

